      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- INDUSTRIES WE SERVE -->
  <section class="thinking">
    <div class="wrap">
      <header class="section__head">
        <div>
          <div class="eyebrow">Where we work</div>
          <h2 class="section__title" style="margin-top:1.25rem;">
            Sectors we know <em>from the inside.</em>
          </h2>
        </div>
        <p class="lead">
          Twenty years across complex delivery means we don't need three weeks
          to learn how your sector procures, reports or escalates. We've been in
          the room.
        </p>
      </header>

      <div class="thinking__grid">
        <div class="think-card" style="border-top-color:var(--ochre);">
          <div class="think-card__kicker">Sector 01</div>
          <h3 class="think-card__title">Media &amp; broadcasting</h3>
          <p class="think-card__desc">
            Led four workstreams under CIDO governance at the ABC, running two
