          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="think-card" style="border-top-color:var(--ochre);">
          <div class="think-card__kicker">Sector 02</div>
          <h3 class="think-card__title">Higher education</h3>
          <p class="think-card__desc">
            A decade across three Australian universities - Griffith,
